				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Does it take an enchanter to clear these things up? Let me enlighten all of you on this quest:<BR>
The Steel Warrior named Larn Brugal expects the weapons to be delivered from Groflah's forge.  Groflah's delivery man was killed by orcs while coming from (God Knows Where) in the West.  You take the voucher from Larn to Groflah to find this out.  Groflah tells you that there are four raw short swords, each numbered individually.  Give all four raw short swords to Larn Brugal, and he gives you a Reward Raw Short Sword, which Groflah sharpens when you give it to him.  This act results in Groflah's Stoutbite, I know not the stats of this weapon, but you can probably find such info on someone's site.<BR>
<BR>
Misteri<BR>
Enchantress of the 8th Circle<BR>
